premise_source_doc_sentence: The University of Antioquia  (  Universidad de Antioquia  )  , also called UdeA , is a public , departmental , coeducational , research university located primarily in the city of Medellín , Antioquia , Colombia , with regional campuses in Amalfi , Andes , Caucasia , Carmen de Viboral , Envigado , Puerto Berrío , Santa Fe de Antioquia , Segovia , Sonsón , Turbo and Yarumal .
